c: 12
v: 26
t: "Nabii Yuusuf tet dirabboysak is (zuleykha kinnuk) isi nafsî fan dalwah yoh secteeh anu woh teetik cineeh umaaneh teetit faxem mayyu iyye, tokkel tet marak saldiy handuulut (sarollole kinnuk) yani kaah sumaaqite, tokkel kay kamis foocak qanxisimek is numma teceeh usuk dirableelak numuk teyna kinni iyye"